Data Wrangling :
It  is a process of doing the transformation of our data from one form to another form.

Transformation includes:
1.Categorical data to numerical data.
  Categorical data is data which is not numeric and generally called
  as object in data frame
2.Existing numerical data to to standarized or normalized data.
3.Extracting new column and transforming  it.Eg we can make a new column  from two column )
(datetime column from date and  time column)


Categorical to Numerical data Conversion:

Libraries used for transformation
1.Pandas
2.sklearn(scikit-learn)

Specific Function:
pandas.get_dummies()
pandas.map()
from sklearn.preprocessing import LabelEncoder
from sklearn.preprocessing import OrdinalEncoder
from sklearn.preprocessing import OneHotEncoder


Numerical to Standardized data

Libraries used for transformation
1.Pandas
2.sklearn(scikit-learn)

Specific Function:
from sklearn.preprocessing import StandardScaler
from sklearn.preprocessing import MinMaxScaler


